        26,
        70,
        543,
        80
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 5,
      "serial_label": "L5",
      "text": "scribed Communist party of Greece, is trying to make the",
      "char_len": 56,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        88,
        543,
        98
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 6,
      "serial_label": "L6",
      "text": "municipal elections scheduled for 5 April a test of the pro-West-",
      "char_len": 65,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        106,
        543,
        138
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 7,
      "serial_label": "L7",
      "text": "ern government's popularity.",
      "char_len": 28,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        142,
        543,
        156
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 8,
      "serial_label": "L8",
      "text": "",
      "char_len": 0,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        160,
        543,
        170
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 9,
      "serial_label": "L9",
      "text": "EDA leaders are seeking collaboration of non-Communist",
      "char_len": 54,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        177,
        543,
        189
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 10,
      "serial_label": "L10",
      "text": "opposition parties in sponsoring joint slates of candidates for",
      "char_len": 63,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        197,
        543,
        207
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 11,
      "serial_label": "L11",
      "text": "the municipal councils. While EDA has been rebuffed by spokes-",
      "char_len": 62,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        214,
        543,
        225
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 12,
      "serial_label": "L12",
      "text": "men for several minor nationalist opposition parties, it appar-",
      "char_len": 63,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        230,
        543,
        242
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 13,
      "serial_label": "BL13",
      "text": "",
      "char_len": 0,
      "line_kind": "blankline",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        243,
        543,
        266
      ]
    },
    {
