        267,
        543,
        286
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 15,
      "serial_label": "L15",
      "text": "ently has achieved some success with Liberal leader Sophocles",
      "char_len": 61,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        287,
        543,
        297
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 16,
      "serial_label": "L16",
      "text": "Venízelos.",
      "char_len": 10,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        305,
        543,
        315
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 17,
      "serial_label": "L17",
      "text": "",
      "char_len": 0,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        323,
        543,
        333
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 18,
      "serial_label": "L18",
      "text": "This co-",
      "char_len": 8,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        341,
        543,
        373
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 19,
      "serial_label": "L19",
      "text": "operation, even if not effective in the council elections, may",
      "char_len": 62,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        377,
        543,
        387
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 20,
      "serial_label": "L20",
      "text": "become evident in the subsequent election of mayors by the",
      "char_len": 58,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        395,
        543,
        405
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 21,
      "serial_label": "L21",
      "text": "councillors.",
      "char_len": 12,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        413,
        543,
        423
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 22,
      "serial_label": "L22",
      "text": "",
      "char_len": 0,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        431,
        543,
        444
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 23,
      "serial_label": "L23",
      "text": "Venízelos, however, is spokesman for only one faction of",
      "char_len": 56,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        449,
        543,
        460
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 24,
      "serial_label": "L24",
      "text": "the rapidly deteriorating Liberal party. Several prominent",
      "char_len": 58,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        467,
        543,
        477
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 25,
      "serial_label": "L25",
      "text": "Liberals have denounced collaboration with EDA and are work-",
      "char_len": 60,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        485,
        543,
        495
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 26,
      "serial_label": "PB26",
      "text": "",
      "char_len": 0,
      "line_kind": "paragraphblank",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        501,
        543,
        520
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 27,
      "serial_label": "L27",
      "text": "ing with other nationalist leaders to defeat the Communists.",
      "char_len": 60,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        521,
        543,
        531
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 28,
      "serial_label": "L28",
      "text": "This grouping may hold the balance of power in some cities if",
      "char_len": 61,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        539,
        543,
        549
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 29,
      "serial_label": "L29",
      "text": "the elections result in approximately equal distribution of coun-",
      "char_len": 65,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        557,
        543,
        567
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 30,
      "serial_label": "L30",
      "text": "cil seats between EDA and the government.",
      "char_len": 41,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        575,
        543,
        585
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 31,
      "serial_label": "L31",
      "text": "",
      "char_len": 0,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        593,
        543,
        603
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 32,
      "serial_label": "L32",
      "text": "The government favors holding \"nonpolitical\" elections,",
      "char_len": 55,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        611,
        543,
        621
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 33,
      "serial_label": "L33",
      "text": "--emphasizing candidates rather than parties--apparently for fear",
      "char_len": 65,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        630,
        543,
        640
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 34,
      "serial_label": "L34",
      "text": "that EDA, which captured 25 percent of the popular vote in the",
      "char_len": 62,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        648,
        543,
        658
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 35,
      "serial_label": "L35",
      "text": "general elections in May 1958, has continued to gain strength",
      "char_len": 61,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        26,
        665,
        543,
        675
      ]
    },
    {
      "line_1based": 36,
      "serial_label": "PB36",
      "text": "",
      "char_len": 0,
      "line_kind": "paragraphblank",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
